{"type":"message","id":"bb6c4460","parentId":"1454708c","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:23:47.940Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is reporting an issue with their Confluence setup. They mention that when they set up a user, they enter their Confluence API key, email, API token, and bot token, but when they go to use it, the data hasn't been received and it's still their (the user's) data that needs to be fixed.\n\nThis is a bug report about the DTLX or QLHV system - specifically about the setup/configuration flow where user-provided credentials aren't being properly saved/loaded.\n\nLet me think about what this could be referring to:\n- Confluence MCP credentials setup\n- The DTLX system (which uses confluence-dtlx MCP)\n\n\n- The QLHV system (which uses confluence-qlhv MCP)\n- Or possibly the openclaw-tui setup\n\nLooking at the context, the user has been working on DTLX and QLHV systems with various cron jobs and API configurations. This sounds like the user tried to set up their own Confluence API credentials in the system but the configuration isn't being picked up - it's still showing the old/system's default data instead of the user's credentials. The most likely issue is that the credentials aren't being properly saved to the configuration file or environment variables, or there's a caching issue preventing the new credentials from loading.\n\nI need to clarify which system this is affecting and check the relevant configuration files to see where the credentials should be stored.","thinkingSignature":"2ea31495a8cb0454fffde0b6e7f265ff7e4d572127461538ebb2d15d53de85b7"},{"type":"text","text":"Để tôi kiểm tra file config credentials xem dữ liệu đang được lưu ở đâu.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_058emdogz0nv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review -name \"*.json\" | xargs grep -l \"api.key\\|apikey\\|apiKey\\|CONFLUENCE_API\\|CONFLUENCE_TOKEN\\|BOT_TOKEN\" 2>/dev/null | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_058emdogz0nv_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/ 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":343,"output":444,"cacheRead":11571,"cacheWrite":11608,"totalTokens":23966,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776255812251,"responseId":"062eb6459a299007015610fd2221395b"}}
