{"type":"message","id":"ba3a93d3","parentId":"a26c1753","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:30:04.470Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is that `install.sh` passes `--team` to `ahv-setup.js`, but when running via pipe, it needs to also pass `--yes` to skip all interactive confirmations.\n\nThe fix: detect non-TTY and add `--yes` to the ahv-setup.js call.","thinkingSignature":"12f96ede73f1b058c6ffb749224241014fe223800e85e7a623bac7be2f903af0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rblnk0vkgx7f_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/install.sh","edits":[{"oldText":"  # Run setup\n  local team=\"${1:-dev}\"\n  step \"Chay setup cho team: $team...\"\n  node bin/ahv-setup.js --team \"$team\"","newText":"  # Run setup\n  local team=\"${1:-dev}\"\n  step \"Chay setup cho team: $team...\"\n  # Auto-skip confirmations when running via pipe (stdin already consumed by curl)\n  local skipFlag=\"\"\n  if [ ! -t 0 ]; then\n    skipFlag=\"--yes\"\n    info \"Detected piped mode — auto-skipping prompts\"\n  fi\n  node bin/ahv-setup.js --team \"$team\" $skipFlag"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":404,"output":284,"cacheRead":48683,"cacheWrite":473,"totalTokens":49844,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776256198662,"responseId":"062eb7c7dd665b959e8638eff747f911"}}
