{"type":"message","id":"de042c76","parentId":"d0548eb5","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:30:51.724Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me also update install.sh to show a better usage message for piped mode without team specified. Actually, since the fix defaults to \"dev\" automatically, the script will just run with team dev. Let me also add a `info` log in install.sh showing what team was selected in piped mode.Actually, the install.sh already logs the team. The key fix is the `--yes` flag being added automatically.Let me also update the install.sh header to show how to use with team selection.","thinkingSignature":"7ad85ac2ebc0d0c1b521120effd16ac1679852db5633849c49efcd20d47b14a3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_p1lvdixiz5m7_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-openclaw-setup/install.sh","offset":1,"limit":12}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":179,"output":171,"cacheRead":52228,"cacheWrite":701,"totalTokens":53279,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776256246360,"responseId":"062eb7f738aef9fffeacf07ded6286c8"}}
