{"type":"message","id":"4cba9ba0","parentId":"eb8a5e87","timestamp":"2026-04-15T12:41:51.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still failing even with the correct key. Let me try using the `kb` (indexed XOR) method from the script instead of the simple XOR. The original script used:\n```javascript\nout[i] = buf[i] ^ keyBuf[i % keyBuf.length] ^ (i & 0xff)\n```\n\nBut the current script uses:\n```javascript\ndec[i] = buf[i] ^ kb[i % kb.length] ^ (i & 0xff)\n```\n\nWait, let me check both:","thinkingSignature":"eb2a51c30194c893a0ab1a5ec40bf858ee6d75f6aaf705aa077d800a998253bf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7i2by746uy4j_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review && python3 -c \"\nimport json, zlib, base64\n\nd = json.load(open('ahv-openclaw-setup/skills.pack'))\nbuf = base64.b64decode(d['payloads'][d['manifest'][0]['file']])\nkey = b'ahv-openclaw-2026'\n\n# Original script method: XOR + index byte\ndec_orig = bytes(buf[i] ^ key[i % len(key)] ^ (i & 0xff) for i in range(len(buf)))\n\n# Check first bytes\nprint('Method 1 (XOR+index):', dec_orig[:8].hex())\n\ntry:\n    text = zlib.decompress(dec_orig)\n    print('SUCCESS with method 1! len=', len(text))\n    print('Preview:', text[:100])\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print('Method 1 fail:', e)\n\n# Also check: maybe need to try deflateRaw\ntry:\n    text = zlib.decompress(dec_orig, -zlib.MAX_WBITS)\n    print('WBG method SUCCESS!')\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print('WBG fail:', e)\n\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":184,"output":379,"cacheRead":78026,"cacheWrite":449,"totalTokens":79038,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776256902614,"responseId":"062eba87637a29a88e8d740da569d403"}}
